Class 3: 
i) Motor Cars <= 3000 kg with <= 7 passengers, exclusive of the driver; 
ii) and Motor Tractors and other Motor Vehicles <= 2500 kg.

Class 3A: 
i) Motor Cars without clutch pedals <= 3000 kg with <= 7 passengers, exclusive of the driver; 
ii) and Motor Tractors and other Motor Vehicles without clutch pedals of unladen weight <= 2500 kg.
